@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vaghwa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.72) - ((v0 + 0.71 - tmp + 0.55) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.99)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.28 - v0 + 0.54)) - (0.49 - tmp))
    v1 = (0.46 * (wp.sin(v0 + 0.24) / wp.sin(tmp + 0.99)))
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.06)) + v1)
    data[tid] = v0
